    "Title": "Should'a left it to a professional",
    "Description": "We had this kid named ~mission(TargetName) volunteer to go take out some XenoThreat near ~mission(Location|Address). Everything we knew about the place said it was gonna be too much for ~mission(TargetName|Last) to handle, but they were real keen on boosting their standing with the Headhunters and thought this would do it, so they went alone.\n\nHaven't heard anything but XenoThreat comms coming out of that place since. If you want to go and knock it over, we'll pay you instead. If you can find out what happened to ~mission(TargetName|Last) that would be a bonus.\n\nStows out.",
